&quot;Well we better get back and recharge. The Preds may go for a counter offensive.&quot;

He transformes and starts to drive off towards base. He goes slower to keep up with the rest of the troops.

OOC: Kup had already been ordered back to base remember?

::Kup::

He still walked through the base looking for the problem. Then he saw it. A chunk of the base was blown away. Parts of bots layed all over. He could see the left overs of Sunhawk, and three bots he wasn&#39;t sure about. Most likely Preds that had been captured.

He opened a comm to Talos.

&quot;This is Kup reporting in from the base. There has been a explosion here. A part of the base has been blown away. I have what I think to be four destroyed bots here. I believe one of them to be Sunhawk.&quot;

